{% extends "layouts/app-layout.njk" %}

{% set pageTitle = "Backlog of components and patterns" %}
{% set pageSection = "Community and contribution" %}
{% set pageDescription = "The service manual is built on the research and experience of many digital teams in the NHS. We have a shared backlog and encourage people to contribute." %}
{% set dateUpdated = "July 2026" %}

{% block beforeContent %}
  {% include "community-and-contribution/_breadcrumb.njk" %}
{% endblock %}

{% block bodyContent %}

  <p>Anyone can:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>propose, develop or contribute to new components or patterns</li>
    <li>suggest improvements to anything in the design system or other parts of the service manual</li>
  </ul>

  <p>Our community backlog is held on GitHub, an open collaboration space we use. It's split into 3 sections:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="https://github.com/orgs/nhsuk/projects/21/views/1">design system (styles, components and patterns) backlog <span class="nhsuk-u-visually-hidden"> on GitHub</span></a></li>
    <li><a href="https://github.com/orgs/nhsuk/projects/20/views/1">content guide backlog <span class="nhsuk-u-visually-hidden"> on GitHub</span></a></li>
    <li><a href="https://github.com/orgs/nhsuk/projects/19/views/1">practices and ways of working backlog <span class="nhsuk-u-visually-hidden"> on GitHub</span></a> – includes Accessibility guidance and the NHS service standard</li>
  </ul>

  <p>Issues in the backlog can be:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>proposed</strong> – someone has suggested a new component or pattern</li>
    <li><strong>to do</strong> – the proposed component or pattern has been agreed and is ready to work on</li>
    <li><strong>in progress</strong> – someone is actively working on the component or pattern</li>
    <li><strong>published</strong></li>
  </ul>

{% endblock %}
